data.description: HOME IS AVAILABLE TO SHOW. SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY. You're sure to fall in love with this spacious ranch-style home sitting on a .54 acre corner lot within a quiet Kronenwetter neighborhood. Experience the sensation of residing beyond the city, yet conveniently close to shopping areas nestled between Mosinee and Wausau. As you approach the front entrance, you'll be greeted by a delightful garden area bursting with vibrant flowers and lush shrubbery during the summer months. Stepping through the front door, you'll be welcomed by a generous foyer that leads into the capacious living room. Turning to the right, you'll discover four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary bedroom boasts its own walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. Ascending a set of stairs to your right, you'll find a bonus room tucked away in the lower level. The basement offers ample space, with the potential to be customized into an additional family room. To the left of the living room, a luminous and roomy kitchen awaits, complete with a fireplace to add warmth and charm.,The patio door leads to a secluded backyard featuring a deck. The two car garage has two back doors that open directly to the deck and on to the side of the garage. The detached garage measures around 30x24 and includes a manual 16' overhead door. The garage is divided into two sections: an insulated and heated 11x23 workshop area with an overhead loft. An additional electrical panel is in place for further possibilities. The shingles on the detached garage remain the original ones from its construction year. Conversely, the house's shingles were replaced a few years back in 2022. The water heater was also swapped out in 2013. This residence holds significant untapped potential. Ensure you arrange a viewing before it's too late!
